Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.65,0:00:05.69,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,注意时机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.71,0:00:07.41,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,快夺走我的穿透能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.13,0:00:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就靠你了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.23,0:00:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天该隼翼哥做早饭吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.55,0:00:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 抱歉
