Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 步未
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你几岁了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.37,0:00:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现年八岁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.39,0:00:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们会在三年后被抓走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.32,0:00:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿越时光的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先去找熊耳等人做伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了并肩战斗 这是在未来许下的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.47,0:00:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熊耳找到了我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.21,0:00:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒出来个很厉害的能力者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:00:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.63,0:01:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 你说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.98,0:01:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是一起发过誓 要改变世界的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂密友啊 知道不！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.25,0:01:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该知道我的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.27,0:01:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 心里也该有底了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…我们在未来见过？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.68,0:01:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全正确！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.95,0:01:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算在未来见过 现在还是陌生人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.74,0:01:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这么黏我！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.14,0:01:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛 好见外啊 维尼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维尼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小熊维尼嘛 我叫习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.44,0:01:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然会接受这种外号？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熊耳已经组建了能力者的小团体
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我按照计划 跟着熊耳去见其他成员
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.39,0:02:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是时光回溯能力者 乙坂隼翼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.13,0:02:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说…也是白搭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他在未来也见过你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁信这种鬼话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的能力是穿透 能穿过障碍物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 单单穿过一堵墙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会让你筋疲力尽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 目时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.77,0:02:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是催眠能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让对象睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但自己也会随后陷入沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 前泊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能精确消除特定的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.98,0:02:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 必须接触对方的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花很多时间去搜寻记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说完了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全正确
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是熊耳先告诉他的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说你连熊耳都不信 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你专程从未来赶来 找我们有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 我道出了能力者们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在未来步入的凄惨末路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.26,0:03:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了我的故事 伙伴们的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我们一起 在未来制定的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所能采取的手段只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.97,0:03:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要聚集能力者 自己保护自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 我们开始建设
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只属于能力者的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这终究只是个孩子团
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论重来多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都没能保护好自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到后来 还有成员发起狂来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击研究设施 想要解救伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们缺少守护的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底 只有小孩是办不成事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借助大人的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人？鬼才会相信大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法使用能力的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能理解我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原能力者又如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有几个熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该值得一试
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 既然你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 具体该怎么做？隼翼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 让我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维尼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼翼哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你15岁生日快乐！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:28.34,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该使用时光回溯了 否则就会被抓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就趁现在 来抽超巨型彩票吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年的大奖 总金额高达…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六亿日元！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六亿？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有六亿日元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许就能让大人出力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实不止六亿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要使用我的能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只能走这条路了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:04:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集资金吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:04:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:04:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我回到过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去收集赛马 乐透 各种赌博信息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后聚集更多能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组建让科学家下不了手的大组织
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要听这家伙使唤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七野 相信隼翼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们过去见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又得重新解释一遍 真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时光回溯后的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看着镜子 感觉到不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个能力…每次使用都会损耗视力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后 我们召集伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制定了搜罗巨款的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 这也需要我反复时光回溯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的视力也越来越弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.09,0:05:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会将至今为止映入眼睛的物品 人 风景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都压缩成一个瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后回溯至过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以一旦失明 能力就无法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心里很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又被研究设施抢了先
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是第几次了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像最近总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 就变成能力者争夺战了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼翼 我们需要能保护他们的环境吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.09,0:06:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…让我想想方案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维尼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知过了多少次生日了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能保护他们的环境…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的存在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.19,0:06:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 哥哥要升学考试了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想去哪所高中？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 可以这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有宇 你的点子太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都没说啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再回去一次 维尼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能收集资金的组织已经建成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 还是没能保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这样你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:07:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再回去一次 我肯定会失明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这是最后的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这最后的机会 你要用来做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要建学校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的能力 青春期一过就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 建个在青春期里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护能力者的学校就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也能保护能力出现前的有宇和步未
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这真的是最后一搏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会完全失去视力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 事在人为嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是老样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失明后的我 你也要好好找出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵 包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我进行了最后的时光回溯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 失去了光明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:08:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着 我在黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和熊耳等人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这条终极之路上走了下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后 我们收购了一个学校法人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是件劳神费心的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但大家的欢呼声 洗去了我的疲劳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后就好办了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们才刚起步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 维尼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有两件事要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我消除有宇和步未关于我的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不这么做 我以后就没法自由行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不能再抛头露面了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 以后只能在幕后活着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我在日本各处建立同样的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建立保护能力者的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:08:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要保护我们目不能及的那些能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的长相广为人知 可就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 就用你的长发把脸遮起来吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对哦 再淋点水 就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的淋水了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.19,0:09:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼翼哥哥 你去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好担心你的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我还带了朋友来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:49.63,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,我去收拾房间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:51.73,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…啊啊 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:52.51,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目时 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步未妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步未？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前泊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后的未来 已经没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安安心心地生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远爱你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 我离开了你和步未
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 说完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反复时光回溯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建立现在这个教育机构…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能来得及救奈绪的哥哥 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里 他正在逐渐康复 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来 关于哥哥的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都被能力消除了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连视力都没了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试过 果然不能再回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 还有件事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事必须做到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们之间的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要救步未…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 该怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你的掠夺能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺走我的时光回溯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掠夺？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个词 在梦里出现过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺走能力者的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和高城都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.21,0:11:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的能力 早就被他看透了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:12:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能力是 掠夺特殊能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 居然有这种能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太强力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先得去调查一下掠夺能力的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都要小心行事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调查后发现 你误解了自己的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是在单纯地入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入侵对象 其实是你夺取能力的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证据就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你至今为止入侵过的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都失去了能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 何必大张旗鼓地说服能力者？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我去入侵一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就完事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕对方是特殊能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做也有违人道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得有必要让对方知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「为什么不可以使用能力」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 不断夺取能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会让你变成相当危险的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己一直没察觉 还真是万幸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是奈绪 你真懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的能力应该还在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要夺取它 然后回到过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救步未
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到步未能力发作的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去之后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺取步未身上的危险能力「崩毁」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这段经过告诉一无所知的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以…救回步未
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就靠你了 有宇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 为了拯救步未
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//----------------------------TXTB----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步未…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是几号？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 回到这一天了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能力是 崩毁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是怎样的能力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能将盯上的东西毁坏之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 位置呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在学校的配套公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能插句话么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:14:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那恐怕是我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么依据吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她感冒了 没来上学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时间还留在家里的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定就是我妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敏锐得异乎寻常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不像平时的你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 反正我们不是科学家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先去给步未妹妹探探病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便探探她有没有获得能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 她生着病呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要去太多人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友利 你一个人来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想…你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小步未 多保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥大人 给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是她么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待您再次光临本店
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去送送她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:15:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咻咻咻～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没交往啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问出噩梦的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这或许会成为「崩毁」能力的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 友利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我说我来自未来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会相信吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是会为步未做这种事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就省事多了 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后天 步未会因「崩毁」能力而死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了阻止这场悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我穿越时光 回来救她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 鉴于你办事能力有限
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生会也要帮这个忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能对你有误解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:16:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去步未之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自暴自弃 自甘堕落
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那时拯救我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你 友利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来的事情 我当然没有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 既然你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然让我遭了不少罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你总是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 晚安的说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 再等会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你施个治感冒的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安然无恙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 步未就没有能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 还有件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家时再来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒刚好 可别勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.34,0:18:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小别片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键的时候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要小心行事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能搞到校服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 你又在搞啥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我看起来一点也不像初中生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就装扮成教师了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢？就这样进去？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想作为步未的哥哥 出现在对手面前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想法 这样很有威慑力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 拜托各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙坂同学妹妹的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定会拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺带一提
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不存在「拯救生命」的小魔法！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.53,0:18:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:52.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从后门进
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你是这里的学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我是本校教师 有事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来没见过你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来趟办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 不对 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.82,0:19:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我去 我跟你去！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转眼就少了个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 还有友利和柚咲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 难道你是柚咲琳？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你认错了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.90,0:19:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么看都是柚咲琳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 柚咲琳转来我们学校啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱首歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比电视上还漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老娘不是柚咲琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么看都是柚咲琳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你再看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咳…呸呸呸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶像会干这种事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.11,0:19:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊…这些唾液我该怎么对待？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好恶心！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这女孩也好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和柚咲琳一样 也是偶像吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是来拍片的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:20:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 柚咲琳上高中了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 臭丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别自顾自地逃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人的变装 全都没意义啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你转进来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.69,0:20:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,及川同学他就像忘了我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼里变得只有你！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.18,0:20:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.51,0:20:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:20:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才会遭殃！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.08,0:21:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有宇哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.86,0:21:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓你一吓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再敢伤害我妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让你尝尝更厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.43,0:21:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听懂了吗？快滚！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险过去了 我们回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.79,0:21:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人叫妹控也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:21:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再失去步未
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.23,0:22:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 这么快就来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.74,0:22:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熊耳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗬 你认识我？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维尼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,省了不少事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.91,0:22:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你妹妹一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.66,0:22:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.71,0:22:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哥哥身边
